---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Link } from "../components/Link";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Swarnim Walavalkar — Work"
  description="Things I've done in the past"
>
  <main class="prose">
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-12">
      <!-- Devfolio -->
      <section class="group">
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            <a href="https://devfolio.co/" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">Devfolio</a>
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-900/40 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-300 border border-emerald-800/50">Current</span>
            <time class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Since 2023</time>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
          Building an economic opportunities platform for builders, through
          fellowships, hackathons, bounties and more...
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://x.com/SwarnimVW/status/1883830860182679566"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >Learned a ton</a> about how <a
              href="https://devfolio.co/blog/ethindia-2024-playing-the-infinite-game-of-ethereum/"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >large scale technical events</a> are hosted
          </li>
          <li>
            Improved and built new internal tools to help the ops team manage
            event logistics better
          </li>
          <li>
            Hacked on top of interesting new web3 primitives like <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://attest.sh/"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >EAS attestations</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Helped build and ship industry defining initiatives like <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://devfolio.co/blog/onchain-credentials-helping-you-put-your-proof-of-work-on-the-blockchain/"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >onchain credentials</a>, <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://devfolio.co/blog/previewing-crypto-cheer/"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >crypto cheer</a>, and <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://devfolio.co/blog/introooducing-quadratic-voting-on-devfolio/"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >quadratic voting</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://x.com/SwarnimVW/status/1893925130180682102"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >Championed</a>, <a
              href="https://x.com/SwarnimVW/status/1686352773120655360"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >built</a>, and <a
              href="https://x.com/SwarnimVW/status/1818206013931303265"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >shipped</a> a bunch of product features
          </li>
          <li>
            Led engineering for <a
              href="https://x.com/devfolio/status/1893836929826996426"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
            >Devfolio AI</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Shipped lots of cool software with cool people. Made some great
            friends. :)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="border-t border-neutral-800/60"></div>

      <!-- Now&Me -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            <a href="https://nowandme.com/" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">Now&Me</a>
          </h3>
          <time class="text-sm text-neutral-500 tabular-nums">2022 — 2023</time>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
          A peer-to-peer mental health platform
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
          <li>Learned a ton about building community/social apps</li>
          <li>Learned a ton about product analytics + user behavior analysis</li>
          <li>Learned a ton about building scalable Kubernetes infra</li>
          <li>Built robust internal tools for UGC moderation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="border-t border-neutral-800/60"></div>

      <!-- COVID Army -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            <a href="https://github.com/covidarmy/" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">COVID Army</a>
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-900/30 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-300 border border-sky-800/40">Public Good</span>
            <time class="text-sm text-neutral-500 tabular-nums">2021</time>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
          A platform to find lifesaving COVID related resources across 1200
          indian cities at the height of the COVID 19 pandemic
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/covidarmy" class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400">github.com/covidarmy</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="border-t border-neutral-800/60"></div>

      <!-- Cato TV -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            <a href="https://github.com/catoverse/" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">Cato TV</a>
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-indigo-900/30 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-indigo-300 border border-indigo-800/40">Open Source</span>
            <time class="text-sm text-neutral-500 tabular-nums">2021 — 2022</time>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
          An ambitious education video platform, that aimed to curate the best
          knowledge on the internet.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">
          This was my first time working in a team, Learned a ton; about
          engineering, product and people.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">
          Built cool shit with incredible people and fostered some of my closest
          friendships
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">
          We bit off more than we could chew at the time, the product
          unfortunately never came to fruition.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/catoverse" class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400">github.com/catoverse</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="border-t border-neutral-800/60"></div>

      <!-- Navgurukul Labs -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">
            Navgurukul Labs
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-900/30 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-300 border border-sky-800/40">Public Good</span>
            <time class="text-sm text-neutral-500 tabular-nums">Early 2022</time>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
          Got in touch with Navgurukul through friends at Cato, Cato was briefly
          a part of Navgurukul Labs before we ultimately decided to move on...
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">
          Briefly volunteered to help with engineering and some misc product
          management for various initiatives within the org.
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
          <li>
            Led the Cato TV engineering team for a while (poorly). I was
            clueless. Learned a ton
          </li>
          <li>Learned to be a product-focused engineer</li>
          <li>Started to build a product intuition</li>
          <li>
            Learned the importance of talking to users, and not building in a
            void
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
